Thursday’s area sports briefs (Oct. 8) 
From staff reports 
St. James girls golf defeated the North Myrtle Beach Chiefs in their final match of the regular season 161-249. Smith Knaffle earned medalist honors for the Shark at Eagles Nest with a 38. 
SJ: Smith Knaffle 38; Kelli Smith 39; Jordan White 41; and Steely Hays 43 
NMB: Gabby Spoone 50; Laura van der Hevnel 63; Emma Keiner 68; Stephanie Kelly 68 High school girls volleyball 
▪ Myrtle Beach 3, St. James 0 (25-20, 25-20, 25-13)
